      <strong style="color:#E0DCD8;">Remember:</strong> This is a self-reflection tool, not a clinical diagnosis. If your scores feel significant, consider speaking with a qualified professional.
    </div>
    <div class="nd-results-buttons">
      <button class="nd-btn-primary" id="ndCopyCSVBtn">Copy Results for Spreadsheet</button><br />
      <button class="nd-btn-secondary" id="ndRetakeBtn">Retake Assessment</button>
      <button class="nd-btn-secondary" id="ndCloseBtn2">Close</button>
